	<script>
		$(document).ready(function() {
			var AJAX_LIKE_REQ_PATH_PREFIX 		= "/01619458-9ea4-41aa-b99e-1ee0023073e5/";
			var ACTION_WARN						= 2;
			var ACTION_REASON_TIME_ALLOWANCE	= 4;
			var uniqueToken						= '895c420e4d12428ef9d451609f73a2b1569feff4';
			var originalUrl						= 'http://www.tell-my-ip.com/index.html';
			var userPoliciesWithOverride		= [{"avatar":"","displayName":"Jon","policyId":12,"userName":"jomal88@gmail.com"},{"avatar":"","displayName":"Kpuc","policyId":11,"userName":"Kpuc"}]
;
			var arr								= '';
			var defaultAvatar					= '';
			var selectedPolicyUserName 			= '';
			var	cachedAuthPolicyPassword		= null;
			var action							= 3;
			var reason							= 1;
			var minutesRemainingToday			= 90;

			//	enable traditional JSON serialization
			jQuery.ajaxSettings.traditional = true;

			//	set logo banners
			$("img.logoBannerImage").attr("src", "data:image/png;base64,");

			function getAjaxRequestURL(methodName) {
				var currentUrl	= $.mobile.activePage.data('url');
				var parsed		= $.mobile.path.parseUrl(currentUrl);
				return $.mobile.path.makeUrlAbsolute(AJAX_LIKE_REQ_PATH_PREFIX + methodName, parsed.domain);
			}
			
			//	make our request change link friendly to resizing
			var continueButtonWidth = $("#buttonContinue").outerWidth(true) + $("#buttonGoBack").outerWidth(true) + 10;
			$("#spanReqChange").width($(window).width() - continueButtonWidth);

			//	hide continue button if not appropriate
			if((ACTION_REASON_TIME_ALLOWANCE != reason) && 
				(0 == userPoliciesWithOverride.length) && 
				(ACTION_WARN !== action))
			{
				$("#buttonContinue").hide();
			}
			
			$(window).resize(function () {
				$("#spanReqChange").width($(window).width() - continueButtonWidth);
			});

			//	request change handler
			$(document).on("vclick", "#requestLink", function() {
				var payload = {
					'token' : uniqueToken,
					'arr'	: arr
				};

				$.getJSON(getAjaxRequestURL('request_change'), payload, function(data) {
					if(data.rc) {
						$("#popupRequestChangeSuccess").popup();	//	init
						$("#popupRequestChangeSuccess").popup("open");
						$("#spanReqChange").hide();
					}
				})
				.error(function() {
					$("#popupInternalError").popup();	//	init
					$("#popupInternalError").popup("open");
				});
			});

			$(document).on("vclick", "#submitUserFeedbackLink", function() {
				$.mobile.changePage("#pageSendUserFeedback", { transition : "slide" });
			});

			//	go back button handler
			$(document).on("vclick", "#buttonGoBack", function() {
				if ((document.layers) || (document.getElementById && !document.all)) {
					var pages = history.length-1;
				} else { 
					var pages = history.length;
				} 
				if(pages > 0) {
					history.back();
				} else {
					window.location = 'about:blank';
				}
			});

			//	continue button handler. Transitions to auth page if non-warn
			if(ACTION_WARN === action) {
				$(document).on("vclick", "#buttonContinue", function() {
					var payload = {
						'token'				: uniqueToken,
						'arr'				: arr
					};
					$.getJSON(getAjaxRequestURL('warn_override'), payload, function(data) {
						if(data.rc) {
							window.location = originalUrl;
						}
					});					
				});
			} else {
				$(document).on("vclick", "#buttonContinue", function() {
					$.mobile.changePage("#pagePolicyAuthForContinue", { transition : "slide" });
				});
			}

			//	user feedback page
			$(document).delegate("#pageSendUserFeedback", "pageinit", function() {
				$("#formSendUserFeedback").submit(function() {
					var userComments = $("#textUserFeedbackComments").val();

					var payload = {
						'userComments'	: userComments,
						'arr'			: arr
					};

					$.getJSON(getAjaxRequestURL("submit_user_feedback"), payload, function(data) {
						$("#spanSubmitUserFeedback").hide();
						$.mobile.changePage("#pageMain", { transition : "slide" });
					})
					.error(function() {
						$("#popupInternalError").popup();	//	init
						$("#popupInternalError").popup("open");
					});					

					return false;	//	handled by us
				});
			});

			//	init handler for Time Allowance extend page
			$(document).delegate("#pageTimeAllowanceExtend", "pageinit", function() {
				$("#sliderTimeAllowanceExtend").on("slidestop", function(event, ui) {
					if(event.target.value >= minutesRemainingToday) {
						newVal = "Until the end of today";
					} else {
						var time = new Date(0, 0, 0, 0, event.target.value, 0, 0);
						h = time.getHours();
						m = time.getMinutes();
						if(h > 0) {
							newVal = h + ' hours, ' + m + ' minutes';
						} else {
							newVal = m + ' minutes';
						}
					}
					$("#spanTimeAllowanceExtendValue").html(newVal);
				});

				$("#sliderTimeAllowanceExtend").attr("max", function() {
					return ((minutesRemainingToday / 5) + (minutesRemainingToday % 5 > 0 ? 1 : 0)) * 5;
				});

				//	Time Allowance extend submit handler
				$("#formTimeAllowanceExtendCommit").submit(function() {
					var extendMinutes	= $("#sliderTimeAllowanceExtend").val();
					
					var payload = {
						'username'	: selectedPolicyUserName,
						'password'	: cachedAuthPolicyPassword,
						'extendMin'	: extendMinutes,
						'arr'		: arr
					};

					$.getJSON(getAjaxRequestURL("time_allowance_extend"), payload, function(data) {
						if(data.rc) {
							window.location = originalUrl;
						}
					})
					.error(function() {
						$("#popupInternalError").popup();	//	init
						$("#popupInternalError").popup("open");
					});

					return false;	//	handled ourselves
				});
			});

			//	init handler for auth login to continue page
			$(document).delegate("#pagePolicyAuthForContinue", "pageinit", function() {
				$("#popupAuthFailed").popup();	//	init

				//	authenticate for continue past block/etc.
				function authenticateOverridePermission(un, pw, callback) {
					var payload = {
						'token'		: uniqueToken,
						'username'	: un,
						'password'	: pw,
						'arr'		: arr
					};
					$.getJSON(getAjaxRequestURL('block_override'), payload, function(data) {
						callback(data.rc);
					})
					.error(function() {
						$("#popupInternalError").popup();	//	init
						$("#popupInternalError").popup("open");
					});
				}
				
				//	auth submit handler
				$("#formAuth").submit(function() {
					var userName 				= selectedPolicyUserName;
					cachedAuthPolicyPassword	= $("#inputAuthPassword").val();
					$("#inputAuthPassword").val("");	//	clear it
					$('#passwordEntryArea').hide();
					$('#authPleaseWait').show();

					authenticateOverridePermission(userName, cachedAuthPolicyPassword, function(result) {
						if(result) {
							if(ACTION_REASON_TIME_ALLOWANCE === reason) {
								$.mobile.changePage("#pageTimeAllowanceExtend", { transition : "slide" });
							} else {
								window.location = originalUrl;
							}
						} else {
							$("#popupAuthFailed").popup();	//	init
							$("#popupAuthFailed").popup("open");
							$("#passwordEntryArea").show();
							$("#authPleaseWait").hide();
						}
					});
					return false;	//	we handle this all ourselves
				});

				//	populate and bind users
				function populateAvailUserPolicies(into, list) {
					$.each(list, function() {
						var avatarBase64 = '';
						if('' == this.avatar) {
							avatarBase64 = defaultAvatar;
						} else {
							avatarBase64 = this.avatar;
						}

						into.append('<li><div class="avatarAndDispName"><a id=userPolicy_' + this.policyId  + ' class="policyAvatar" href="#" title="' + this.displayName + '"><img src="data:image/png;base64,' + avatarBase64 + '" width="96" height="96" border="0" /></a><p>' + this.displayName + '</p></div></li>');
						$('#userPolicy_' + this.policyId).data('policy', this);
					});
				}

				populateAvailUserPolicies($("#policyList"), userPoliciesWithOverride);

				$('#liquid1').liquidcarousel({
					height		: 135, 
					duration	: 100, 
					hidearrows	: true
				});

				function onAvatarFocusOrClick(o) {
					$('#passwordEntryArea').fadeIn(500);
					selectedPolicyUserName = o.data('policy').userName;

					$('.policyAvatarSelected').removeClass('policyAvatarSelected').addClass('policyAvatar');
					o.addClass('policyAvatarSelected').removeClass('policyAvatar');

					$("#inputAuthPassword").val("");	//	clear it
					$('#inputAuthPassword').focus();
				}

				$('.policyAvatar').focus(function() {
					onAvatarFocusOrClick($(this));
				});

				$('.policyAvatar').click(function() {
					onAvatarFocusOrClick($(this));
				});

				$('.policyAvatar:focus').click(function() {
					onAvatarFocusOrClick($(this));
				});

				$('#inputAuthPassword').focus(function() {
					if(/Android|iPhone|iPad|iPod/i.test(navigator.userAgent)) {
						$('#buffer').show();
						$("html,body").scrollTop($("#inputAuthPassword").offset().top, "slow");
					}
				});
				$('#inputAuthPassword').blur(function() {
					$('#buffer').hide();
				});

				//	start out hidden
				$('#passwordEntryArea').hide();
				$('#authPleaseWait').hide();
				$('#buffer').hide();
			});

			$(document).delegate("#pagePolicyAuthForContinue", "pageshow", function() {
				$('#liquid1').resize();	//	hack
			});

			$(document).delegate("#pagePolicyAuthForContinue", "pagehide", function() {
				$('#passwordEntryArea').hide();
			});

			//	try and cause browser to hide address bar
			window.scrollTo(0,1);
		});
	</script>
</head>
<body>
	<!-- popups/etc. -->
	<div data-role="popup" id="popupInternalError" class="ui-content" data-theme="b" style="max-width:350px;">
		Oops\! An internal error has occurred.
	</div>

	<div data-role="popup" id="popupAuthFailed" class="ui-content" data-theme="b" style="max-width:350px;">
		Authentication failed!
	</div>

	<div data-role="popup" id="popupRequestChangeSuccess" class="ui-content" data-theme="b" style="max-width:350px;">
		Your request has been submitted and is available for your parent or administrator to review in the Net Nanny admin console.
	</div>

	<!-- pages -->
	<div data-role="page" id="pageMain">
		<div class="logoBannerArea">
			<img alt="Net Nanny" class="logoBannerImage" />
		</div>

		<div data-role="content">
			<h4 style="color:#e7582f">The website requested has been Blocked for the following reason(s):</h4>
			<p><i>Proxy</i></p>
		</div>

		<div data-role="collapsible" data-collapsed="true" style="padding-left:10px; padding-right:10px; visibility: visible;">
			<h3>Details</h3>
			<p><textarea readonly="readonly" cols="40" style="overflow-x: auto; word-wrap: break-word;">URL: http://www.tell-my-ip.com/index.html</textarea></p>
		</div>

		<div data-role="content" style="font-size: x-small">
			<span id="spanSubmitUserFeedback">
				<a id="submitUserFeedbackLink" data-role="none" href="#">Submit categorization feedback to Net Nanny</a>
			</span>
		</div>

		<div data-position="fixed" class="ui-bar" data-role="footer">
			<div class="ui-grid-a ui-responsive">
				<div class="ui-block-a">
					<div class="ui-body ui-body-d" style="">
						<span id="spanReqChange"><a id="requestLink" data-role="none" href="#">Request to change how this website is treated in the future</a></span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="ui-block-b" data-theme="none">
					<div class="ui-body ui-body-d">
						<a id="buttonContinue" data-transition="slide" style="float: right; margin-right:27px; visibility: visible;" data-role="button" data-icon="arrow-r" accesskey="1" title="Access Key: 1">Continue</a>
						<a id="buttonGoBack" style="float: right; margin-right:10px;" data-role="button" data-icon="arrow-l" accesskey="2" title="Access Key: 2">Back</a>	
					</div>
				</div>
			</div> 	
		</div> 
	</div>

	<div data-role="page" id="pagePolicyAuthForContinue">
		<div class="logoBannerArea">
			<img alt="Net Nanny" class="logoBannerImage" />
		</div>

		<div data-role="content">
			<h4 style="color:#e7582f">Authentication required</h4>
			<p>An administrator is required to continue. Please select a user or click cancel.</p>
		</div>

		<div data-role="content" id="liquidContainer">
			<div id="liquid1" class="liquid">
				<span class="previous"></span>
				<div class="wrapper">
					<ul id="policyList">
						<!-- dynamic -->
					</ul>
				</div>
				<span class="next"></span>
			</div>

			<br/>
			<div style="width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto">
				<div id="passwordEntryArea">
					<form id="formAuth">
						<span style="float:left; min-width:100px;"><input type="password" name="pass" id="inputAuthPassword" value="" placeholder="password" data-theme="a" data-inline="true"/></span>
						<span style="float:left; margin-left:10px; margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px;"><button type="submit" data-inline="true" data-mini="true" accesskey="3" title="Access Key: 3">Continue</button></span>
					</form>
					<div id="forgotPassword" style="font-size:smaller; font-weight:lighter; clear:both;"><a href="https://www.netnanny.com/link/lostpassword">Forgot Password</a></div>
				</div>
				<span id="authPleaseWait">Logging in. Please wait...</span>
				<div id="buffer" style="height:150px"></div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div data-position="fixed" class="ui-bar" data-role="footer">
			<a data-rel="back" style="float: right; margin-right:27px;" data-role="button" data-icon="delete" accesskey="4" title="Access Key: 4">Cancel</a>	
		</div>
	</div>

	<div data-role="page" id="pageTimeAllowanceExtend">
		<div class="logoBannerArea">
			<img alt="Net Nanny" class="logoBannerImage" />
		</div>

		<div data-role="content">
			<h4 style="color:#e7582f">Extend Time Allowance</h4>
			<p>Slide to adjust how long to <i>temporarily</i> extend Time Allowance for today</p>
		</div>

		<div data-role="content" style="width: 50%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
			<div id="spanTimeAllowanceExtendValue" style="margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">5 minutes</div>
			<input type="range" id="sliderTimeAllowanceExtend" value="5" min="5" max="0" step="5" data-highlight="true" class="ui-hidden-accessible" data-theme="c">
			<div align="right">
				<form id="formTimeAllowanceExtendCommit">
					<button type="submit" data-inline="true" data-mini="true" accesskey="3" title="Access Key: 3">Continue</button>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div data-position="fixed" class="ui-bar" data-role="footer">
			<a data-rel="back" style="float: right; margin-right:27px;" data-role="button" data-icon="delete" accesskey="4" title="Access Key: 4">Cancel</a>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div data-role="page" id="pageSendUserFeedback">
		<div class="logoBannerArea">
			<img alt="Net Nanny" class="logoBannerImage" />
		</div>

		<div data-role="content">
			<h4 style="color: #e7582f">Let us know how we're doing</h4>
			<p>Please add any comments &#8210; if this page is miscategorized, let us know!</p>
		</div>

		<div data-role="content">
			<form id="formSendUserFeedback">
				<div align="right">
					<textarea name="textUserFeedbackComments" id="textUserFeedbackComments" rows="5"></textarea>
					<button type="submit" data-inline="true" data-mini="true" accesskey="3" title="Access Key: 3">Submit</button>
				</div>
			</form>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
